Package: bayesS4
Date: 2018-06-28
Type: Package
Title: Bayes Classification of Spetrometric Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Asmita Poddar & Florent Latimier
Maintainer: Asmita Poddar & Florent Latimier <asmita.podar@gmail.com>
Depends:
